---
title: Sausage and Roasted Pepper Ragù with Spaghetti
description: This twist on classic spaghetti bolognese is packed with tender ground sausage and tons of herby, garlicky flavour, all topped with a sprinkling of fresh Parmesan. It'll have everyone in your home going back for more!
